Input: Non-Ontological Resource 
•
The European Training Thesaurus (ETT) constitutes the controlled 
vocabulary of reference in the field of vocational education and training 
(VET) in Europe. The relation semantics between the sub-ordinate and 
the super-ordinate concepts is subClassOf. 
•
This thesaurus is available at http://libserver.cedefop.europa.eu/ett/en/
